<pane xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="http://jmri.org/xml/schema/programmer.xsd">
  <name>Legacy Function Map</name>
  <name xml:lang="ca">Mapejat de funcions (legacy)</name>
  <name xml:lang="cs">Přiřazení funkcí (legacy)</name>
  <name xml:lang="da">Funktions Indstillinger (legacy)</name>
  <name xml:lang="de">Funktionszuordnung (legacy)</name>
  <name xml:lang="fr">Carte des Fonctions (classique)</name>
  <name xml:lang="it">Mappa Funzioni (legacy)</name>
  <name xml:lang="nl">Funktietoewijzing (legacy)</name>
  <column>
    <row>
      <column>
        <label>
          <text>&lt;html&gt;
            &lt;h1&gt;Note: Use of this pane is not recommended.&lt;/h1&gt;
             &lt;br/&gt;
             &lt;br/&gt;
           &lt;strong&gt;
              The CVs in this pane can be used to map a limited range of effects to functions F0-F12 and are included to
                &lt;br/&gt;
              remain consistent with NMRA Standards for DCC Configuration Variables (S-9.2.2, p.7).
              &lt;br/&gt;
              &lt;br/&gt;
              &lt;em&gt;
                Note 1: CVs 33-46 are set to values of 0 by default, offer a secondary method of function mapping,
                &lt;br/&gt;
                and are not used to determine this SoundCar decoder's default function assignments.
              &lt;/em&gt;
              &lt;br/&gt;
              &lt;br/&gt;
              &lt;em&gt;
                Note 2: Some sound effects might not be implemented as shown on this legacy function map.
                &lt;br/&gt;
                It is displayed as is for consistency with former SoundCar versions.
              &lt;/em&gt;
            &lt;/strong&gt;
            &lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;h2&gt;&lt;em&gt;
              Any check marks on this pane will override settings on the main Function Map pane!
            &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
          &lt;/html&gt;</text>
        </label>
        <label>
          <text> </text>
        </label>
        <label>
          <text>Use this sheet to determine which functions will control which outputs</text>
          <text xml:lang="ca">Usa aquesta pestanya per establir quina funció controla cada sortida</text>
          <text xml:lang="cs">Použijte tento list pro určení která funkce bude řídit který výstup</text>
          <text xml:lang="de">Hier einstellen, welche Funktion welchen Ausgang steuert</text>
          <text xml:lang="fr">Utiliser cette feuille pour déterminer quelles fonctions contrôlent quelles entrées</text>
          <text xml:lang="it">Usa questo foglio per programmare quale Funzione contolla quale uscita</text>
          <text xml:lang="nl">Stel per uitgang de aanstuurfunctie in</text>
        </label>
        <label>
          <text> </text>
        </label>
      </column>
    </row>
